<h2 class="hardwired" id="hardwired">
HARDWIRED
</h2>
<div class="name" id="name">
<p>
*Depend Upon Hardware.<br> 
*Used By RISC.<br>   
*Diagnose Is Hard.<br>
*Complex Structure.<br>
*No Use Of Memory.<br>
*difficulty occurs In complex instructions.<br>
*Fast Speed.<br>
*No AI's And Technology Used.<br>
*Non-Reprogrammable.<br>
*Software Can't Be Updated.<br>
</p>
</div>
<img src="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/1-9.jpg" height="300">
<div class="line" id="line"></div>

<h2 class="hardwired" id="hardwired">
MICRO-PROGRAMMED
</h2>
<p id="name" class="name">
    *Depend Upon Software.<br> 
    *Used By CISC.<br>   
    *Diagnose Is Easy.<br>
    *Simple Structure.<br>
    *Memory Is Used.<br>
    *No difficulty occurs In complex instructions.<br>
    *Slow Speed.<br>
    *AI's And Technology Are Both  Used.<br>
    *Reprogrammable.<br>
    *Software Can Be Updated.<br>
    </p>
    <img src="https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/controlunit.png" height="300">
